== Overview ==

Dragon Warrior II features 86 unique monsters across the game's expanded world. This page documents their stats and drop tables.

== Monster Data Structure ==

Each monster entry is 10 bytes:

{| class="wikitable"
|-
! Offset !! Size !! Description
|-
| $00 || 1 || Strength
|-
| $01 || 1 || Agility
|-
| $02-$03 || 2 || HP
|-
| $04 || 1 || Attack pattern
|-
| $05 || 1 || Defense
|-
| $06 || 1 || Spell pattern
|-
| $07 || 1 || Magic resistance
|-
| $08-$09 || 2 || Experience
|-
| $0A-$0B || 2 || Gold
|}

