== Special Monsters ==

=== Metal Slime ===
* Very high agility and defense
* Immune to most spells
* High flee rate
* Worth 1015 EXP

=== Metal Babble ===
* Even higher stats than Metal Slime
* Worth 10015 EXP
* Extremely rare

